      "stem": "下列程式以 eps=0.5、min_pts=4 對 5 個點做 DBSCAN 分類(計鄰居數,並判定 core/border/noise)。每點不含自己,但 core 判定加 1(自身)。請逐行追蹤。",
      "code_block": "import numpy as np\npoints = np.array([[0.0, 0.0], [0.2, 0.0], [0.0, 0.2], [0.4, 0.4], [10.0, 10.0]])\neps = 0.5\nmin_pts = 4\ncounts = []\nfor i in range(len(points)):\n    c = sum(1 for j in range(len(points)) if i != j and np.linalg.norm(points[i] - points[j]) <= eps)\n    counts.append(c)\nlabels = []\nfor i in range(len(points)):\n    if counts[i] + 1 >= min_pts:\n        labels.append('core')\n    else:\n        is_border = any(i != j and counts[j] + 1 >= min_pts and np.linalg.norm(points[i] - points[j]) <= eps for j in range(len(points)))\n        labels.append('border' if is_border else 'noise')",
